REBUILD 商业许可协议
09/03/2019


概述

1. 本协议是对 REBUILD 的商业许可的说明。
2. REBUILD 使用开源（GPL-3.0）和商用双重许可授权。适用何种授权取决于您使用 REBUILD 的目的。
3. 在您使用 REBUILD 前应当认真阅读并同意本协议之内容/条款。
4. 如您不同意本协议之内容/条款，应该立即停止使用。继续使用 REBUILD 则视为同意本协议之全部内容/条款。
5. REBUILD 已申请软件著作权，任何不遵守本协议的使用都是侵占知识产权行为，需要承担相应的法律后果。


符合以下情况可以免费使用

1. 仍旧作为开源项目（需采用 GPL-3.0 开源协议）。
2. 出于非商业/非盈利目的的使用。
3. 个人/企业/组织内部使用，不限制是否出于商业目的，但不能对 REBUILD 进行任何形式的销售/赠与/分发。


有偿使用

1. 如果您希望对 REBUILD 进行 OEM 或任何形式的销售/赠与/分发。
2. 如果您希望获得 REBUILD 的官方售后服务和技术支持。


如您对本协议有任何异议，请联系我们 https://getrebuild.com/




REBUILD Commercial License Agreement (English version)
September 3, 2019


Overview

1. This Agreement is a description of the commercial license for REBUILD.
2. REBUILD uses open source (GPL-3.0) and commercial dual licenses. Which authorization is available depends on the purpose for which you use REBUILD.
3. You should carefully read and agree to the contents/terms of this Agreement before you use REBUILD.
4. If you do not agree to the content/terms of this Agreement, you should stop using it immediately. Continued use of REBUILD is deemed to be in agreement with the entire content/terms of this Agreement.
5. REBUILD has applied for the right to file software. Any non-compliance with the use of this agreement is an act of encroachment on intellectual property rights and requires corresponding legal consequences.


Free for use if the following conditions are met

1. Still as an open source project (requires GPL-3.0 open source agreement).
2. Use for non-commercial/non-profit purposes.
3. Individual/enterprise/organization internal use, not limited to commercial purposes, but cannot be used for any form of sales/gift/distribution of REBUILD.


Paid use

1. If you wish to OEM or any form of sales/gift/distribution of REBUILD.
2. If you want to get the official after-sales service and technical support of REBUILD.


If you have any objections to this agreement, please contact us at https://getrebuild.com/